Introduction

Nana is a South Korean singer and Actress signed with H Music Entertainment. Nana is the Leader, Main Dancer, Lead Vocalist, Lead Rapper & Visual of the girl group WOOAH (formerly known as woo!ah!). She is also a member of the project girl group EL7Z UP.

She made her debut as a member of WOOAH on May 15, 2020, with the group's first single album "Exclamation". That same year, she also made her debut as an actress with the drama “No Going Back Romance.” She continued her acting career with roles in the dramas “Best Mistake Season 3” (2021), “Mimicus” (2022) and "Fall for You" (2022).

On April 24, 2023, Nana participated in the survival show Queendom Puzzle and finished in 2nd place earning her spot in the project girl group EL7Z UP. They made their debut on September 14, 2023, with their first mini album “7+Up”.
